# Component Rules

- Max 200 lines per component file
- Sub-components in same directory as parent
- Props passed down — no direct global state access in children
- CSS custom properties for all dynamic styling
- Use CSS animations over Framer Motion when possible (performance)
- @media (hover: hover) for all hover effects (touch device safety)
